Step 1:
   Go to: /apache/conf/httpd.conf
   Uncomment "Include conf/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf"
Step 2:
   Go to: /apache/conf/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf
   Insert at the bottom:
        <VirtualHost *:80>
          ServerAdmin yii@gmail.com
          DocumentRoot "C:\wamp\www\YII"
          ServerName  yii
          <Directory "C:\wamp\www\YII">
              Options FollowSymLinks
              AllowOverride All
              DirectoryIndex index.php
              Require all granted
              Order deny,allow
          </Directory>
      </VirtualHost>
Step 3:
   Go to windows/system32/drivers/etc/hosts
   Add 127.0.0.1 yourdomain.com at the bottom.
Step 4:
   Restart apache.
